data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET with updates! VA, FHA, Conventional financing eligible. Deland Home with a BIG personality! This 2200+ sq ft home sits on a 1/2 acre lot and is just minutes from downtown and Stetson University. The main living space is a true open concept, split floorplan, with oversized bedrooms and a private Florida room off the main bedroom. Freshly painted in the main living space with a neutral color palette. Insurance won't be an issue with a METAL ROOF, NATURAL GAS, TANKLESS WATER HEATER, a brick FIREPLACE, and SOLAR PANELS to help keep your energy costs low in the Florida summers- only $30 power bill to Duke for solar connection. If you're looking for energy efficient, close to downtown, and sick of the cookie-cutter spec homes, this is definitely the one see!
